name: PharmacyInterventions
title: PharmacyInterventions
description: This value set is intended to be used in the Pharmacist eCare Plan.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This grouping value set contains codes representing any type of pharmacist intervention that may be performed during an encounter.),(Data Element Scope: Datatype: Procedures and Situations. The intent of the terms in this value set is to document any type of intervention. These codes are documented separately from the explicit action taken place to execute an order within a system, and are used for intervention tracking.),(Inclusion Criteria: Any codes that represent a pharmacist intervention performed during an encounter.),(Exclusion Criteria: Any codes that do not represent an intervention that could be preformed during an encounter.)
